#
#   AX_RUBY_EXTENSION(extname[, fatal, ruby])
#
# DESCRIPTION
#
#   Checks for Ruby extension.
#
#   If fatal is non-empty then absence of a the extension will trigger an error.
#   The third parameter can be used to specify the ruby to use.
